reviewText: I have attended several greek step shows at Florida A&M University or FAMU as they call it.  Their step shows are always one of the most anticipated during homecoming.  This show did not disappoint.  I was amazed at the number of greek fraternities and sororities that attend this university.  Overall, each step team did very well.
